rComments: Barry is sometimes too kind but always genuine. His passion for everything, even classwork, that he works on is infectious. This man can make you love topics you previously hated in a way that isn't obnoxious or overbearing. He always listens to and cares about his student as well. Barry Freeman is the kind of professor every department needs.

Inspiring professor and lovely person. His passion and kindness engage you in the material and make you want to try your best. Always an interesting and pleasant learning experience with Barry. Very true that he notices and rewards hard work and engagement.

Barry is the most inspiring hard working professor I've ever had. His courses are always hard work but they push you to improve and thrive in unconventional ways, and he is always in your corner cheering you on.  Barry sees how hard you work for your marks and incorporates that as well so push yourself!
Pretty clear about everything, just make sure you listen to everything he says in class and put it to use when performing.
